    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-center">
          <div class="lg:col-12 md:col-12 mb-8">
            <h2>My Favorite Project</h2>
            <div class="container my-4">
              <div class="row gap-4">
                <div
                  class="col-12 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col gap-4"
                >
                  <h5><strong>BadBoyz (Rackoo)</strong></h5>
                  <div class="flex gap-8">
                    <div class="card-image">
                      <img src="/images/rackoo.png" alt="project" width="600" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-[1.2rem]">
                      <p>
                        <strong>Badboy</strong> is a project designed for pairing
                        players in badminton games, with support for multiple courts.
                        It was originally created for use among friends during badminton
                        sessions. Currently, there are plans to rebrand the app as
                        <em>Rackoo</em> to enhance mobile compatibility.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        The app is built using Vue, Express, and MongoDB, with
                        potential future plans to transition to Go as the
                        backend.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-end gap-2">
                    <a
                      class="btn btn-primary my-4"
                      href="https://badminton.atipnasakun.online/room/659bbdf2e21783acc96e76ab"
                      >Application</a
                    >
                    <a
                      href="https://github.com/atippaz/pwa-badboyz"
                      class="btn btn-primary my-4">Repository</a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="col-12 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col gap-4"
                >
                  <h5><strong>32Controller x TicTacToe Game</strong></h5>
                  <div class="flex gap-8">
                    <div class="card-image">
                      <img
                        src="/images/32controller.jpg"
                        alt="project"
                        width="800"
                      />
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-[1.2rem]">
                      <p>
                        The <strong>32Controller x TicTacToe Game</strong> is a project
                        that integrates various technologies, combining IoT and web
                        applications. The IoT device, an Arduino-based 32 controller,
                        is used to control the TicTacToe game.
                      </p>
                      <p>
                        The technologies involved include <em
                          >Arduino, C, MQTT protocol, Socket, Vue, Express,
                          Nginx, Docker, HTTPS</em
                        >, and a custom domain. After completing the program, I
                        set up a personal VPS and deployed the application,
                        using Nginx and Docker for the deployment. The server
                        was also configured with HTTPS for security, and reverse
                        proxy was implemented for improved traffic handling.
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex justify-end gap-2">
                    <a
                      href="https://github.com/atippaz/32-game-controller"
                      class="btn btn-primary my-4">Repository</a
                    >
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div
                  class="col-12 border border-slate-400 rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col gap-4"
                >
                  <h5><strong>BomberMan</strong></h5>
                  <div class="flex gap-8">
                    <div class="card-image">
